                            </a>
                            <!-- YouTube -->
                            <a href="#" class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-lg bg-primary text-white hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M23.498 6.186a3.016 3.016 0 0 0-2.122-2.136C19.505 3.545 12 3.545 12 3.545s-7.505 0-9.377.505A3.017 3.017 0 0 0 .502 6.186C0 8.07 0 12 0 12s0 3.93.502 5.814a3.016 3.016 0 0 0 2.122 2.136c1.871.505 9.376.505 9.376.505s7.505 0 9.377-.505a3.015 3.015 0 0 0 2.122-2.136C24 15.93 24 12 24 12s0-3.93-.502-5.814zM9.545 15.568V8.432L15.818 12l-6.273 3.568z"/></svg>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- COLUMNA DERECHA: MAPA -->
                <div class="h-96 md:h-full min-h-96 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
                    <iframe 
                        src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3900.5742903045477!2d-77.10236592346873!3d-12.108343588724186!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x9105d5a1d3d3d3d3%3A0x1234567890abcdef!2sCalle%20German%20Schreiber%20276%2C%20Lima!5e0!3m2!1ses!2spe!4v1234567890123" 
                        width="100%" 
                        height="100%" 
                        style="border:0;" 
                        allowfullscreen="" 
                        loading="lazy" 
                        referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
                    </iframe>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECCIÓN: ENLACES A OTRAS PÁGINAS (CTA ADICIONAL) -->
    <section class="bg-white py-16 md:py-24">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">
                    Nuestra Identidad y Compromiso
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                    Descubra cómo nuestra trayectoria y experiencia se traducen en soluciones estratégicas para su negocio.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Grid de Enlaces -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
                <!-- Card 1: Visión e Historia -->
                <a href="/nosotros/vision-historia" class="group">
                    <div class="relative h-64 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-primary/5 flex items-center justify-center hover:from-primary/30 hover:to-primary/10">
                        <div class="text-center px-6">
                            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-primary mx-auto mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
                            </svg>
                            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300">
                                Visión e Historia
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-2">
                                Evolución y propósito de nuestra organización
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </a>

                <!-- Card 2: Nuestro Equipo -->
                <a href="/nosotros/equipo" class="group">
                    <div class="relative h-64 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-primary/5 flex items-center justify-center hover:from-primary/30 hover:to-primary/10">
                        <div class="text-center px-6">
                            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-primary mx-auto mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.7" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>                            </svg>
                            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300">
                                Nuestro Equipo
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-2">
                                El capital humano que lidera la excelencia en cada proyecto
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </a>

                <!-- Card 3: Enfoque de Trabajo -->
                <a href="/nosotros/enfoque" class="group">
                    <div class="relative h-64 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-primary/5 flex items-center justify-center hover:from-primary/30 hover:to-primary/10">
                        <div class="text-center px-6">
                            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-primary mx-auto mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"></path>

                            </svg>
                            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300">
                                Enfoque de Trabajo
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-2">
                                Explore los pilares que rigen nuestra metodología y ética profesional
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</Layout>
